Everyone has stories they could go on and on about, talking about the funny things that happen in their lives, but they don't! Who knows why?  \n\nThis blog is designed to help stir some memories, or churn the imagination into realizing that life is SO good.  Let's enjoy it!

Throughout life, we all have situations to make us consider how we got to where we are.  Hell, sometimes they send us scrambling back crazily, wishing there was an escape, but there isn't.  That's when the only other option we have is to sit and laugh 'til the tears come down.  Sometimes we cry with relief, sometimes we cry from embarrassment, sometimes we cry because it's uncontrollably funny, and other times we don't know why---we just do.
